FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1780419953
OL,3,CSearch under way for 11-year-old last
OL,4,Cseen entering river
OL,6,FOther emergency crews from the
OL,7,FNational Police Air Service, South
OL,8,FYorkshire Fire and Rescue Service and
OL,9,Fthe Yorkshire Ambulance Service are
OL,10,Falso in attendance.
OL,12,FPolice say that the boy's family has
OL,13,Fbeen informed and is being supported
OL,14,Fby specially trained officers.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1780419953
OL,3,CSearch under way for 11-year-old last
OL,4,Cseen entering river
OL,6,FDoncaster Response Team Inspector Neil
OL,7,FPryce said "We know, from witnesses
OL,8,Fand items left on the riverbank, where
OL,9,Fthe boy entered the water. Utilising
OL,10,Fspecialist knowledge and skills, a
OL,11,Fcoordinated multi-agency operation is
OL,12,Funderway and we are doing everything
OL,13,Fwe can to find this young man.
OL,15,F"This is a tragic incident and we
OL,16,Funderstand that members of the public
OL,17,Fwant to do all they can to help but we
OL,18,Fmust ask that, for everyone's safety,
OL,19,Fonly those who are involved in our
OL,20,Foperation enter the River Don.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
